node.text: We understood the assignment. Raise your flag! Today in Boston we celebrate the Caribbean Carnivale & Diaspora, and most of all Co-Founder Mrs. Shirley Shillingford #shesroyal for her dedication to the preservation of Caribbean culture & tradition. This event generates joy & revenue as the third lgst such celebration in North America.

node.text: Happy #internationalalopeciaday from our family to yours.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Ayanna Pressley on August 05, 2021 tagging @dollfaceboston, @blackgirlsunscreen, and @boldskinbabe. May be a closeup of 1 person.

node.text: Alopecia totalis realness. No filter. Happy Thursday to the squad. We've no hair, eyebrows or eyelashes but still rock a crown. Shout out to @blackgirlsunscreen for protecting our baldies.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Ayanna Pressley on August 04, 2021. May be an image of 6 people, people sitting, people standing and outdoors.

node.text:
Our movement met the moment with organizing & radical love. As you lift up MOC who held the line to #ExtendTheMoratorium, please include our indefatigable staff. We could do none of this without them.

Thank you to my #ATeam You Work, do good & seek justice. You deliver resources, relief & hope to the #MA7th You've made innumerable personal sacrifices during a govt shut down, impeachment, a pandemic, insurrection & 
more. Thank you for always having the peoples back & mine too.

If dig deep was a person S/O to the dedicated staffs of @CoriBush @AyannaPressley @AOC @IlhanMN @SaraJacobsCA @JamaalBowmanNY @MondaireJones @JimmyGomezCA @MarkTakano @MaxineWaters @RashidaTlaib @pramilajayapal et al who believe in activist leadership & know that #changecantwait

Organizer. Justice seeker. Educator. Freedom fighter.

node.text: I've so many special moments with people each day, people I'm meeting for the very first time & may never see again but the impression they leave on my heart is indelible.This young woman, Hope is one of them. Ps) On Thursdays we wear pink. Shout out to @jprattboutique @dsimagegroup for the fit.
